{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when he found out what was going on, he came, and he took my brother Tsvi over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was very close with the local authorities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that he told them that he needs a teacher-- a Hebrew teacher-- and he almost make my brother legal there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As long as he stayed there, he was, he was OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I'm concerned, I, I, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Either I had another-- my, my-- I should have said in the beginning, I come from a very large family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had eight sisters and a brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were ten in the family and ten on my mother's side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So and they were scattered all over Hungary, Romania, Czechoslovakia and those three because under Austria-Hungary, this was all one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one, one of his sisters lived in Bihor Diosig.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if my, my father contacted them, or they did it on their own.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day two of the-- my cousins, two girls, came, and they said to me, you are hungr-- hungry over here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are going to come to stay with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and they took me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Already by then I was able-- I was able to go to the train station and buy a, a train ticket.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew enough of the language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it wa-- it wasn't-- it wasn't suspicious because usually if you bought for somebody a train ticket, that was already suspicious.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "During the wartime, they were watching, watching these things very carefully.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How much time do we have?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, we managed-- we managed to get to, to-- I managed to get to Bihor Diosig, where my Uncle [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Goldberg lived.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in the wine business.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
